DESCRIPTION:
Allows the user to retrieve pokedex info, moveset info(by generation), a pokemon's stats, evolution chain, and can search for pokemon items. 
 Requires 3 pip3 installs: 
 pip3 install beautifulsoup 
 pip3 install numpy 
 pip3 install tabulate
NAME: Provides pokemon info searches. Ex !pokedex pokemon pikachu
